STATE
v.
Maurice McKINNON. No. 680P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2006. Robert C. Montgomery, Assistant Attorney General, Ben David, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 6th day of December 2005 by Defendant for "Petition for Discretionary Review":
